data.description: A delightful townhome centrally located and move in ready! You are only a short drive to the beaches, I-95, the bustling night life, the medical hospital, and everything else the city has to offer! This three-bedroom townhome offers a private patio, natural lighting, washer and dryer inside the units, two master split bedrooms, ample counter space in the kitchen and many amenities! You also own the land here which is a plus! There are a ton of amenities included for the low HOA fee including gated access. Pets are allowed.. Welcome Home!
